---
<section class="trust-bar">
  <div class="trust-bar-inner">
    <p class="trust-stripe">Backed by <strong>Dennemeyer</strong>, one of the world's leading IP groups, operating across 180+ jurisdictions since 1962.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .trust-bar {
    background: #f7f9fa;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid #e2eaee;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e2eaee;
  }
  .trust-bar-inner { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .trust-stripe {
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--body); line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .trust-stripe strong { color: var(--headline); font-weight: 700; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .trust-bar { padding: 24px 16px; }
    .trust-stripe { font-size: 13px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .trust-bar { padding: 20px 14px; }
    .trust-stripe { font-size: 12px; }
  }
</style>
